definitions.definition: The Walt Disney Company , named after Walt Disney .
examples: Have you seen Disney's latest film?

definitions.definition: Any of the theme parks and vacation resorts operated by Walt Disney Parks and Resorts .
examples: We went to Disney with the kids this summer.

definitions.definition: A town in Mayes County , Oklahoma , United States , named after Wesley E. Disney .
